Funso Adeoti, the first wife to Kazim Adeoti, the new husband of Nollywood actress, Mercy Aigbe, has sent a stern warning to the actress and her husband. She made the call out via a post on her Instagram story, giving her husband 12 hours to do the needful as this would be her last warning. “@Realmercyaigbe @adekazproduction for the last and final time ‘Stop pushing me’. -Advertisement- “Kazim, do the needful, pull it down. You have been warned. 12 hours only.”